lead_paragraph: Chun In-gee welcomes the pressure of making her first defense of an LPGA major at this week's U.S. Women's Open, and the South Korean believes she is on the brink of more grand achievements.

headline.print_headline: Chun Embraces Pressure in U.S. Women's Open Defense
